# Phase 2-A.2 Step 3: goldens are NOT committed (502 MB+ per suite). Layout:
# keep the parent tracked, ignore everything inside, then carve back out the
# per-suite manifest files. The unignore order matters — Git does not descend
# into a fully-ignored parent, so the parent + per-suite directories must be
# explicitly unignored before the manifest pattern can take effect.
!/tests/goldens/
/tests/goldens/**
!/tests/goldens/*/
!/tests/goldens/*/manifest.toml
/rust/smooth_core/target/

# Phase 2-A Sub-stage A disposable PoC (lives at ../smooth-spike-poc/, symlinked)
/spike-poc

